Main styling will style everything for the screen that is above the max width of 1080px or anything that is not styled within a @media tag and or the 
screen does not meet the sizes of the media tag.

Are Screen Size Targeting Standards:
Main,
Max of 1080px and min of 999px in width.
Max of 998px and min of 760px in width.
Max of 667px and min of 600px in width.
Max of 428px and min of 399px in width.
Max of 398px and min of 360px in width.
